  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe [notifier](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/master/beacon_node/client/src/notifier.rs) is printing things like this:\r\n\r\n```\r\nDec 10 00:24:30.035 INFO Syncing                                 distance: 15663 slots (2 days 4 hrs), speed: 0.00 slots/sec, est_time: inf weeks NaN days, peers: 4, service: slot_notifier\r\n``` \r\n\r\nThere must be something off with the float math here, my bad.\r\n",
